precept Test

field test as quantity of 'mass' max '5 kg'
field test2 as integer max 2 optional

state offState initial
state onState 

event toggle initial

in offState omit test

from offState on toggle 
    -> set test = '6 [lb_av]'
    -> transition onState

from onState on toggle when test2 is set and test2 > 0
    -> clear test2
    -> transition offState

from onState on toggle
    -> transition offState